Pornhub is a pornographic video sharing website and the largest pornography site on the Internet .
Pornhub was launched in Montreal , providing professional and amateur photography since 2007 .
Pornhub also has offices and servers in San Francisco , Houston , New Orleans and London .
In March 2010 , Pornhub was bought by Manwin -LRB- now known as MindGeek -RRB- , which owns numerous other pornographic websites .